To build the database:

1. Navigate to this folder in windows terminal. 
2. Log into mysql -- 
			mysql -u root -p 'type your password here, don't include single quotes'
3. If you were able to log into mysql with no errors then we know our credentials were valid
4. Go ahead and exit mysql by typing 'exit' without the quotes
5. Now use the command mysql -u root -p 'your password' < testdatabase.sql

This should build the most recent version of the test database saved in the sql file